Key Django 5.2 Best Practices:
  Minimal settings: Only include necessary INSTALLED_APPS and MIDDLEWARE
  Proper app structure: Use apps.py for app configuration
  Type hints: Use Python typing throughout
  Dataclasses: For clean data structures without ORM
  Function-based views: With proper decorators for REST API
  URL patterns: Proper namespacing and organization
  Security: CSRF, security headers, proper SECRET_KEY handling
  Performance: Caching, efficient data processing
  Error handling: Proper HTTP status codes and error responses